---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="B-Fitness Gym Kanasín — Climatizado y abierto desde las 5 AM"
  description="El gym del centro de Kanasín: sala climatizada, máquinas de sobra e instructores en piso. ⭐ 4.3 con 63 reseñas en Google. Abierto los 7 días."
  slug="b-fitness-gym-kanasin"
  ogImage="/b-fitness-gym-kanasin/img/foto_4.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Unbounded:wght@500;700;900&family=Archivo:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
  favicon="🏋️"
  themeColor="#070a14"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529995086826"}
  telefono={"999 508 6826"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=4129351128097067350&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <div class="page">

    <!-- ============ HERO COMPACTO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <img
        class="hero-bg"
        src="/b-fitness-gym-kanasin/img/foto_1.jpg"
        alt="Zona de cardio de B-Fitness iluminada con luz LED azul: caminadoras, elípticas y bicis de spinning en uso"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <div class="hero-veil" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Gym · Centro de Kanasín</p>
        <div class="led-rail" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">B-Fitness</h1>
        <p class="hero-hook">Sala climatizada, máquinas de sobra y una banda que entrena en serio. Desde las 5:00 de la mañana.</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/529995086826" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="19" height="19" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.2c-1.6 0-3.1-.4-4.4-1.2l-.3-.2-2.9.8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2Zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1-.3-.1-1.1-.4-2-1.2-.8-.7-1.3-1.5-1.4-1.8-.2-.3 0-.4.1-.5l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5.1-.2 0-.4 0-.5l-.8-1.9c-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.3-.9.9-.9 2.1s.9 2.4 1 2.6c.1.2 1.8 2.7 4.3 3.8.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.5.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2-.1-.1-.3-.2-.6-.3Z"/></svg>
            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=4129351128097067350&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 21s-7-5.5-7-11a7 7 0 0 1 14 0c0 5.5-7 11-7 11Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2.5"/></svg>
            Cómo llegar
          </a>
        </div>
        <a class="rating-chip" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=4129351128097067350&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.3 · 63 reseñas en Google
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ MOSAICO (arriba del pliegue) ============ -->
    <section class="mosaic-wrap" aria-label="Fotos del gimnasio">
      <div class="mosaic">
        <figure class="tile t-big" data-rv>
          <img src="/b-fitness-gym-kanasin/img/foto_4.jpg" alt="Vista amplia de la sala de B-Fitness llena de gente entrenando, con lámparas hexagonales en el techo" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>La sala, un día normal</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="tile" data-rv>
          <img src="/b-fitness-gym-kanasin/img/foto_5.jpg" alt="Racks de mancuernas y zona de peso libre con iluminación LED azul" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Peso libre</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="tile" data-rv>
          <img src="/b-fitness-gym-kanasin/img/foto_2.jpg" alt="Clientes de B-Fitness entre las máquinas de la sala" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Zona de máquinas</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="tile" data-rv>
          <img src="/b-fitness-gym-kanasin/img/foto_3.jpg" alt="Cliente entrenando junto a bancos y poleas en B-Fitness" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Bancos y poleas</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <a class="tile t-rating" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=4129351128097067350&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-rv>
          <span class="t-rating-num"><span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.3</span>
          <span class="t-rating-txt">63 reseñas en Google</span>
          <span class="t-rating-link">Leer reseñas →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ SOBRE NOSOTROS ============ -->
    <section class="section" id="sobre">
      <div class="section-inner narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Sobre nosotros</p>
        <div class="led-rail" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h2>Un gym de barrio que no deja de mejorar</h2>
        <p data-rv>Somos B-Fitness, el gimnasio del centro de Kanasín. Aquí se entrena a gusto: la sala está climatizada —que con el calor de Yucatán se agradece—, el equipo se mantiene limpio y hay máquinas de sobra para armar tu rutina completa: cardio, peso libre y aparatos para todo el cuerpo.</p>
        <p data-rv>No nos gusta quedarnos quietos: la sala y el equipo están en constante actualización, y la gente que entrena aquí lo nota. Nuestros instructores andan en piso para echarte la mano, y el trato es el de siempre: cercano, amable y de vez en cuando con algún detalle para quienes entrenan con nosotros.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ SERVICIOS ============ -->
    <section class="section alt" id="adentro">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Lo que encuentras adentro</p>
        <div class="led-rail" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h2>Todo para tu rutina</h2>
        <ul class="services">
          <li data-rv>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 3 4 14h6l-1 7 9-11h-6l1-7Z"/></svg>
            <h3>Zona de cardio</h3>
            <p>Caminadoras, elípticas y bicis de spinning para calentar o soltar todo.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-rv>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.5 6.5v11M3.5 8.5v7M17.5 6.5v11M20.5 8.5v7M6.5 12h11"/></svg>
            <h3>Peso libre</h3>
            <p>Racks de mancuernas, barras y bancos para trabajar a tu ritmo.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-rv>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/></svg>
            <h3>Gran variedad de máquinas</h3>
            <p>Aparatos para cada grupo muscular; lo dicen las reseñas, no nosotros.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-rv>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="3.5"/><path d="M5 20c.8-3.5 3.6-5.5 7-5.5s6.2 2 7 5.5"/></svg>
            <h3>Instructores en piso</h3>
            <p>Buen trato y apoyo con tu técnica cuando lo necesites.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-rv>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v18M12 7l3-3m-3 3L9 4m3 13 3 3m-3-3-3 3M4 12h16M7 9l-3 3 3 3m10-6 3 3-3 3"/></svg>
            <h3>Sala climatizada</h3>
            <p>Entrena fresco aunque afuera esté el calorón de Kanasín.</p>
          </li>
          <li data-rv>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2.5" y="5.5" width="19" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M2.5 10h19"/></svg>
            <h3>Pago con tarjeta</h3>
            <p>Aceptamos tarjetas para que pagar no sea pretexto.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ RESEÑAS ============ -->
    <section class="section" id="resenas">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Lo que dicen en Google</p>
        <div class="led-rail" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h2><span class="star big" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.3 · 63 reseñas</h2>
        <div class="reviews">
          <blockquote class="review" data-rv>
            <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</div>
            <p>“Excelentes maquinas , climatizado. Todo muy limpio, gran variedad de maquinas . Muy bonito lugar y va mejorando.”</p>
            <footer><strong>zule carrillo</strong> · Hace 1 mes</footer>
          </blockquote>
          <blockquote class="review" data-rv>
            <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</div>
            <p>“Es un buen lugar para entrenar, el personal es amable con los clientes y a veces suelen tener detalles con los mismos. El gimnasio está en constante actualización y mejora de mobiliario para sus clientes.”</p>
            <footer><strong>Alesmaragd</strong> · Hace 11 meses</footer>
          </blockquote>
          <blockquote class="review" data-rv>
            <div class="review-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</div>
            <p>“excelente lugar, buen trato y buenos instructores.”</p>
            <footer><strong>Miguel Camara</strong> · Hace 11 meses</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="center">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=4129351128097067350&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="section alt" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Ubicación y horarios</p>
        <div class="led-rail" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h2>Aquí nos encuentras</h2>
        <p class="address" data-rv>C. 19 entre 16 y 18, Centro, 97370 Kanasín, Yuc., México</p>
        <div class="loc-grid">
          <div class="map-frame" data-rv>
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=C.%2019%20entre%2016%20y%2018%2C%20Centro%2C%2097370%20Kanas%C3%ADn%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              width="600" height="400" style="border:0" loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              title="Mapa: B-Fitness gym Kanasín"></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="hours" data-rv>
            <h3>Horarios</h3>
            <div class="hours-scroll">
              <table id="tabla-horarios">
                <tbody>
                  <tr data-day="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>5:00 – 1:30</td></tr>
                  <tr data-day="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>5:00 – 1:30</td></tr>
                  <tr data-day="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>5:00 – 1:30</td></tr>
                  <tr data-day="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>5:00 – 1:30</td></tr>
                  <tr data-day="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>5:00 – 1:30</td></tr>
                  <tr data-day="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>5:00 – 1:30</td></tr>
                  <tr data-day="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>8:00 – 16:00</td></tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
            <p class="hours-note">Horarios en formato de 24 horas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="section cta-band">
      <div class="section-inner narrow center">
        <h2>¿Empezamos hoy?</h2>
        <p>Escríbenos por WhatsApp y resuelve tus dudas antes de venir. Te esperamos en el centro de Kanasín.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/529995086826" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="19" height="19" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.2c-1.6 0-3.1-.4-4.4-1.2l-.3-.2-2.9.8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2Zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1-.3-.1-1.1-.4-2-1.2-.8-.7-1.3-1.5-1.4-1.8-.2-.3 0-.4.1-.5l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5.1-.2 0-.4 0-.5l-.8-1.9c-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.3-.9.9-.9 2.1s.9 2.4 1 2.6c.1.2 1.8 2.7 4.3 3.8.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.5.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2-.1-.1-.3-.2-.6-.3Z"/></svg>
          Mandar WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <p class="footer-name">B-Fitness gym Kanasín</p>
        <p>C. 19 entre 16 y 18, Centro, 97370 Kanasín, Yuc.</p>
        <p><a href="tel:+529995086826">999 508 6826</a></p>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </div>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ExerciseGym",
    "name": "B-Fitness gym Kanasín",
    "telephone": "+52 999 508 6826",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "C. 19 entre 16 y 18, Centro",
      "addressLocality": "Kanasín",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97370",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.3",
      "reviewCount": "63"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Sa 05:00-01:30", "Su 08:00-16:00"],
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/b-fitness-gym-kanasin"
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --ink: #070a14;
      --surface: #0e1428;
      --surface-2: #131a33;
      --led-blue: #3f7dff;
      --led-violet: #8a5cff;
      --ice: #a9e2ff;
      --text: #e9edfb;
      --text-dim: #94a1c3;
      --line: rgba(122, 152, 255, 0.16);
    }

    body { background: var(--ink); }

    .page {
      font-family: 'Archivo', system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .page h1, .page h2, .page h3 {
      font-family: 'Unbounded', 'Archivo', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin: 0 0 0.6em;
    }

    .page a { color: var(--ice); }
    .page :focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--ice);
      outline-offset: 3px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* ---------- Elemento firma: riel LED ---------- */
    .led-rail {
      width: 72px;
      height: 3px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ice), var(--led-blue) 45%, var(--led-violet));
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.85), 0 0 28px rgba(138, 92, 255, 0.4);
    }
    .center .led-rail { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ice);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }

    /* ---------- Botones ---------- */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      padding: 13px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-primary {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--led-blue), var(--led-violet));
      box-shadow: 0 4px 22px rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.45);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.65); }
    .btn-ghost {
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid rgba(169, 226, 255, 0.4);
      background: rgba(14, 20, 40, 0.55);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ice); }

    .star { color: #ffcf4d; }
    .star.big { text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255, 207, 77, 0.5); }

    /* ---------- Hero compacto ---------- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      align-items: end;
      min-height: min(78vh, 620px);
      min-height: min(78svh, 620px);
      isolation: isolate;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 35%;
      z-index: -2;
    }
    .hero-veil {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      background:
        linear-gradient(to top, var(--ink) 4%, rgba(7, 10, 20, 0.72) 45%, rgba(7, 10, 20, 0.35) 75%, rgba(7, 10, 20, 0.55)),
        radial-gradient(120% 60% at 50% 100%, rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.18), transparent 70%);
    }
    .hero-inner {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1060px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 88px 20px 34px;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 11vw, 5.2rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      margin-bottom: 0.25em;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(7, 10, 20, 0.8);
    }
    .hero-hook {
      max-width: 34ch;
      font-size: 1.06rem;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(7, 10, 20, 0.9);
    }
    .hero-ctas {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .rating-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(14, 20, 40, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }

    /* ---------- Mosaico ---------- */
    .mosaic-wrap { padding: 10px 10px 0; }
    .mosaic {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      max-width: 1060px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .tile {
      position: relative;
      margin: 0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--surface);
    }
    .tile img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    }
    .tile figcaption {
      position: absolute;
      left: 10px;
      bottom: 10px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(7, 10, 20, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
    }
    .t-big { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .t-big img { aspect-ratio: 16 / 10; }
    .t-rating {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
      background:
        radial-gradient(80% 70% at 50% 20%, rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.22), transparent 70%),
        var(--surface);
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .t-rating-num {
      font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .t-rating-txt { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.86rem; }
    .t-rating-link {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: var(--ice);
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .mosaic { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
      .t-big { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
      .t-big img { aspect-ratio: auto; height: 100%; }
      .tile img { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
      .t-rating { aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; }
    }

    /* ---------- Secciones ---------- */
    .section { padding: 64px 20px; }
    .section.alt {
      background:
        radial-gradient(90% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.07), transparent 70%),
        var(--surface);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .section-inner { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-inner.narrow { max-width: 680px; }
    .section h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5.4vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; }
    .section p { color: var(--text-dim); }
    .section .address { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- Servicios ---------- */
    .services {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 28px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .services li {
      background: var(--surface-2);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px 16px;
    }
    .services svg { color: var(--ice); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .services h3 { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.4em; }
    .services p { font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0; }
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .services { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
      .services li { padding: 24px 20px; }
    }

    /* ---------- Reseñas ---------- */
    .reviews {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 28px 0 26px;
    }
    .review {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 22px 20px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .review::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ice), var(--led-blue) 45%, var(--led-violet));
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    .review-stars {
      color: #ffcf4d;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .review p { color: var(--text); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0 0 14px; }
    .review footer { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.84rem; }
    .review footer strong { color: var(--ice); font-weight: 600; }
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    }

    /* ---------- Ubicación ---------- */
    .loc-grid { display: grid; gap: 20px; margin-top: 26px; }
    .map-frame {
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .map-frame iframe {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 320px;
      filter: saturate(0.85) contrast(1.02);
    }
    .hours h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .hours-scroll { overflow-x: auto; }
    .hours table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
    }
    .hours th, .hours td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 9px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .hours th { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .hours td { color: var(--text-dim); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .hours tr.today th, .hours tr.today td {
      color: var(--ice);
      background: rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .hours tr.today th::after {
      content: ' · hoy';
      font-size: 0.75em;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .hours-note { font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 10px; }
    @media (min-width: 860px) {
      .loc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; align-items: start; }
      .map-frame iframe { height: 400px; }
    }

    /* ---------- CTA final ---------- */
    .cta-band {
      background:
        radial-gradient(70% 90% at 50% 110%, rgba(138, 92, 255, 0.22), transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(70% 90% at 50% -10%, rgba(63, 125, 255, 0.15), transparent 70%),
        var(--ink);
    }
    .cta-band h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 6vw, 2.4rem); }
    .cta-band p { max-width: 42ch; margin: 0 auto 24px; }

    /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 30px 20px 90px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      background: var(--ink);
    }
    .footer p { margin: 4px 0; }
    .footer-name {
      font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .footer a { color: var(--ice); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ---------- Scroll reveal (solo con JS) ---------- */
    .js-reveal [data-rv] {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(14px);
      transition: opacity 0.55s ease, transform 0.55s ease;
    }
    .js-reveal [data-rv].rv-in {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var today = new Date().getDay();
      var row = document.querySelector('#tabla-horarios tr[data-day="' + today + '"]');
      if (row) row.classList.add('today');

      // Scroll reveal como mejora progresiva
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        document.documentElement.classList.add('js-reveal');
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('rv-in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        document.querySelectorAll('[data-rv]').forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
